@context: Search for a specific dorama and open its video player page
@blueprint: doramy-club-search

1. NAVIGATE to https://doramy.club/
2. WAIT 2
3. Fill 'Поиск' with 'Игра в кальмара'
4. PRESS ENTER
5. WAIT 2
6. VERIFY that 'Игра в кальмара' is present
7. Click 'Игра в кальмара'
8. WAIT 3
9. VERIFY that 'Смотреть онлайн' is present
10. VERIFY that 'Серии' is present
11. DONE.
